cast.original_title: Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison of Belief
cast.overview: GOING CLEAR intimately profiles eight former members of the Church of Scientology, shining a light on how they attract true believers and the things they do in the name of religion.
cast.title: Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison of Belief

cast.overview: Hitman Martin Blank becomes a moving target after he rebuffs a fellow assassin's invitation to form a union. On the advice of his quirky assistant and neurotic psychiatrist, Martin begrudgingly heads out to Grosse Pointe, Michigan for his ten-year high school reunion, where he soon comes across the woman he jilted on prom night.
cast.title: Grosse Pointe Blank

details.biography:
Jenna Elfman (born September 30, 1971, height 5' 10" (1,78 m)) is an American television and film actress. She is known for her role as Dharma on the ABC sitcom Dharma & Greg.
